txt.en: You have defeated many foes gathered at Dûm Boha. This will surely throw the Haradrim into disarray and give the Host of the West a better chance of making it to the Black Gate.
Half-trolls and look-outs are gathered in Dûm Boha in great number. They seem to be waiting for something. Defeat enough of them to throw their plans into disarray.
Defeated many Haradrim look-outs and half-troll executioners.
Enter the enemy encampment of Dûm Boha
The Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should defeat Haradrim look-outs and half-troll executioners.
There is much to be done in the Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha.
